# ========== 自定义阈值示例 ==========
# Custom Threshold Examples
#
# 示例 1：更保守的安全策略
# Example 1: More conservative safety strategy
# moment_warning_threshold,80.0
# moment_alarm_threshold,90.0
#
# 示例 2：标准安全策略
# Example 2: Standard safety strategy
# moment_warning_threshold,85.0
# moment_alarm_threshold,95.0
#
# 示例 3：宽松策略（不推荐）
# Example 3: Relaxed strategy (not recommended)
# moment_warning_threshold,90.0
# moment_alarm_threshold,100.0

# ========== 验证规则 ==========
# Validation Rules
#
# 系统会自动验证以下规则：
# System automatically validates the following rules:
#
# 1. 载荷表不能为空
#    Load table cannot be empty
#
# 2. 所有半径值必须 >= 0
#    All radius values must be >= 0
#
# 3. 所有额定载荷值必须 > 0
#    All rated load values must be > 0
#
# 4. 表项必须按半径升序排列
#    Entries must be sorted by radius in ascending order
#
# 5. 力矩预警阈值必须在 0-100 范围内
#    Moment warning threshold must be within 0-100 range
#
# 6. 力矩报警阈值必须在 0-100 范围内
#    Moment alarm threshold must be within 0-100 range
#
# 7. 力矩报警阈值必须 >= 力矩预警阈值
#    Moment alarm threshold must be >= moment warning threshold
#
# 如果验证失败，系统将拒绝加载配置并保持使用旧配置
# If validation fails, system will reject the configuration and keep using old configuration

# ========== 配置建议 ==========
# Configuration Recommendations
#
# 1. 载荷表应根据起重机制造商提供的性能曲线设置
#    Load table should be set according to crane manufacturer's performance curve
#
# 2. 建议设置足够的数据点以覆盖整个工作范围
#    Recommend setting sufficient data points to cover entire working range
#
# 3. 力矩预警阈值建议设置为 80-90%
#    Moment warning threshold recommended at 80-90%
#
# 4. 力矩报警阈值建议设置为 90-100%
#    Moment alarm threshold recommended at 90-100%
#
# 5. 在修改配置前，建议先备份原文件
#    Recommend backing up original file before modification
#
# 6. 修改后应进行充分测试，确保安全
#    Thoroughly test after modification to ensure safety
